@wp.kernel

    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v1 + (0.25 - (v1 + 0.24 - v0 + 0.67)))
    v0 = wp.cos((v1 / v1))
    tmp = v0
    v1 = (0.96 + (0.04 + tmp))
